name: EnglishDictionary
comment:
English language dictionary. Check word membership and lookup definitions.

@docs checkIsWord, fetchDefinitions, Definition, Error, Config

aliases.name: Config
aliases.comment:
Holds the endpoint of the companion serverless API. To reduce the size of
the Elm package, all of the word definitions are stored in an AWS Lambda
(serverless) API.

aliases.name: Definition
aliases.comment:
A word defition consists of a part of speech (ex, noun) a meaning, and zero
or more short examples.
aliases.type: { partOfSpeech : PartOfSpeech.PartOfSpeech , meaning : String , examples : List String }

types.name: Error
types.comment: Errors can either be Http or misconfiguration (i.e. missing endpoint)

values.name: checkIsWord
values.comment:
Check membership of a word in the English language.

Words up to and including length 5 can be checked without making an Http request
to the backing serverless API.

values.name: fetchDefinitions
values.comment: Fetch a list of definitions associated with the given word.

types.name: PartOfSpeech
types.comment: Part of speech enumeration. Possible positions of a word in a sentence.

values.name: decoder
values.comment: Decodes a part of speech string representation
